Erlunit 0.2.8/alpha - SAMPLES

Read about samples in sample.erl. It is written to be read top down.

Below, you find the results you should get from executing it then: 

$ ./test

- or -

$ erl
1> c(erlunit).
2> c(sample).
3> sample:run().


